# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# CISV Environment Variables
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ── MAPBOX SATELLITE TOKEN ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# REQUIRED for the Mapbox Satellite Streets map style (the default style).
# 
# To get your FREE token:
# 1. Go to https://account.mapbox.com/
# 2. Sign up or log in
# 3. Create a new public token
# 4. Copy it and paste below (replace the placeholder)
# 
# Without this token, the app will fallback to CartoDB Dark Matter base map.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
VITE_MAPBOX_TOKEN=fuckthishsit

# Paste your token above after the = sign
# Example: VITE_MAPBOX_TOKEN=pk.eyJ1IjoieW91cnVzZXJuYW1lIiwiYSI6InlvdXJrZXkifQ.example
